  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Dungeon Mana, where controlling Mana is the key to survival!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this turn-based roguelite RPG, each run is unique: characters are randomly generated with different skills, and your mission is to choose up to three heroes to face a series of intense battles. The combat revolves around managing three colors of mana: red, blue, and green. Master the mana and conquer the dungeons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/dc9151619edb5a0c5af9c3d4316d1f6b.poster.avif?t=1773918847\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/dc9151619edb5a0c5af9c3d4316d1f6b.webm?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/dc9151619edb5a0c5af9c3d4316d1f6b.mp4?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Turn-Based Mana</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, strategy is key. Enjoy a turn-based combat system where players manage their energy with the most vital resource: Mana. Every action requires careful calculation to maximize your turn, ensuring intense and exciting battles. Think carefully, because controlling Mana could be the difference between victory and defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/bdafe95af2c98e1beda5ab667e899b58.poster.avif?t=1773918847\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/bdafe95af2c98e1beda5ab667e899b58.webm?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/bdafe95af2c98e1beda5ab667e899b58.mp4?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Random Character Selection</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dungeon Mana, each run presents a completely new set of randomly generated characters. With unique abilities and unexpected combinations, each choice is crucial for your success. No adventure is the same, as you never know which heroes will be at your disposal and how to best utilize their power in combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/408aba74399ebdcf637bcf66bfb7b407.poster.avif?t=1773918847\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/408aba74399ebdcf637bcf66bfb7b407.webm?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/408aba74399ebdcf637bcf66bfb7b407.mp4?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Select Your Path</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dungeon Mana, your journey won’t be linear. After each battle, you’ll have to make strategic decisions, choosing between two paths, each with different biomes, enemies, and rewards. Will you face tougher challenges for greater rewards, or take the safer path with more moderate prizes? The choice is yours, and each decision will shape the course of your adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/800182d6daff2e8eba64541de38d77d0.poster.avif?t=1773918847\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/800182d6daff2e8eba64541de38d77d0.webm?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/800182d6daff2e8eba64541de38d77d0.mp4?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose Your Rewards Wisely</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dungeon Mana, after each combat, you’ll face the tough task of choosing between different rewards. Each option can enhance your characters in various ways, but only one will suit your strategy best. The decisions you make will influence your success in upcoming battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/1b70d24ce4be6d373d595905419f360c.poster.avif?t=1773918847\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/1b70d24ce4be6d373d595905419f360c.webm?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/1b70d24ce4be6d373d595905419f360c.mp4?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft Items</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dungeon Mana, crafting items is crucial to improving your strategies. As you progress, you’ll collect materials that allow you to create powerful items to help you in various battles. The key to success lies in what you can craft!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/6417f874764a893dd27234e046250d1c.poster.avif?t=1773918847\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/6417f874764a893dd27234e046250d1c.webm?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/6417f874764a893dd27234e046250d1c.mp4?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlockable Content and More!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you advance, you’ll unlock additional content, from characters and skills to new biomes, enemies, and game modes. Every achievement and completed challenge brings you closer to a host of surprises that will keep players engaged over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/43b9d236b9bb37d0e6494cf6da9250f1.poster.avif?t=1773918847\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/43b9d236b9bb37d0e6494cf6da9250f1.webm?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3365400/extras/43b9d236b9bb37d0e6494cf6da9250f1.mp4?t=1773918847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
